gonna sleep in here?

50:14.750 --> 50:16.883
Yeah, yeah.

50:17.014 --> 50:19.799
We're all going to be together.

50:19.929 --> 50:22.845
Is Julie
ever coming back?

50:22.976 --> 50:25.544
