comfortably basking in the sun,

51:02.842 --> 51:04.409
in a beautiful green shire.

51:04.539 --> 51:06.672
As we always do,

51:06.802 --> 51:09.501
let's welcome
our newest family member.

51:09.631 --> 51:10.937
Here's to Julie.

51:11.068 --> 51:12.721
To Julie!

51:15.985 --> 51:17.335
Thank you.

51:17.465 --> 51:19.293
Welcome, kiddo.

51:19.424 --> 51:21.469
Oh, we're glad to have you.
